![image.png](https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/43f4c680-a7ab-4f2d-b233-d37ec40472ce/f7440c7a-cd35-4e5c-b1fe-4623cef995b0/image.png)

κ²°κ³Όλ¥Ό ν™•μΈν•λ©΄ 4λ¬Έμ¥ λ¨λ‘ κ°™μ€ κ°’μ„ λ‚νƒ€λ‚΄λ” κ²ƒμ„ ν™•μΈν•  μ μμ.

```c
#include <stdio.h>
 
int main(void)
{
    int arr2d[2][3] = {
        {10, 20, 30},
        {40, 50, 60},
    };
    int i, j;
 
    for (i = 0; i < 2; i++)
    {
        for (j = 0; j < 3; j++)
        {
            printf("%d ", arr2d[i][j]);
            printf("%d ", (*(arr2d + i))[j]);
            printf("%d ", *(arr2d[i] + j));
            printf("%d\n", *(*(arr2d + i) + j));
        }
    }
 
    return 0;
}
```

